As Christmas approaches, neon Christmas trees lighting up streets can be seen in many countries and people start to prepare for the celebration of Christmas. Let's take a look.

People pose for photos with a Christmas tree on the Grand Place in Brussels, Belgium, on Nov. 28, 2020.(Photo: Xinhua) 

People visit a Christmas market at the Plaza Mayor in Madrid, capital of Spain, Nov. 28, 2020.(Photo: Xinhua) 



A girl takes part in the annual Christmas parade in downtown Wellington, New Zealand, Nov. 28, 2020.(Photo: Xinhua) 



